{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/filemeasureprogresscallback"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"FileMeasureProgressCallback","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = "},{"text":"GFileMeasureProgressCallback","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GFileMeasureProgressCallback"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"These calls are made on a best-effort basis and not all types of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" will support them.  At the minimum, however, one call will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"always be made immediately.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In the case that there is no support, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reporting"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":" (and the other values undefined) and no further calls will be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"made.  Otherwise, the "},{"code":"reporting","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" and the other values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all-zeros during the first (immediate) call.  In this way, you can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"know which type of progress UI to show without a delay.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_file_measure_disk_usage()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" the callback is made directly.  For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_file_measure_disk_usage_async()"},{"type":"text","text":" the callback is made via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"default main context of the calling thread (ie: the same way that the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"final async result would be reported)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currentSize"},{"type":"text","text":" is in the same units as requested by the operation (see"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apparentSize"},{"text":").","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The frequency of the updates is implementation defined, but is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"ideally about once every 200ms.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The last progress callback may or may not be equal to the final","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"result.  Always check the async result to get the final value."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMeasureProgressCallback"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"This callback type is used by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_file_measure_disk_usage()"},{"type":"text","text":" to make"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"periodic progress reports when measuring the amount of disk spaced"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"used by a directory."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO27FileMeasureProgressCallbacka","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FileMeasureProgressCallback"}],"title":"FileMeasureProgressCallback","symbolKind":"typealias","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Typ